WEBVTT

00:03.128 --> 00:05.088
This was their first view of it.

00:05.297 --> 00:07.758
If you don't look too close,
you'd think it was Earth.

00:08.132 --> 00:11.011
Breaking ground on the town hall.

00:11.219 --> 00:13.347
Is that Captain Mitchell?

00:13.805 --> 00:16.767
No, I think that's Mitchell.

00:17.351 --> 00:18.852
Are we there yet?

00:19.811 --> 00:21.980
Three hours, 17 minutes to go, sir.

00:22.189 --> 00:24.483
Travis has been digging
through the archives.

00:24.691 --> 00:26.318
There's tons of data here:

00:26.735 --> 00:28.653
Crew manifests,

00:28.862 --> 00:30.989
survey photos,

00:31.198 --> 00:32.741
weekly status reports.

00:32.949 --> 00:35.160
I was hoping to find something,

00:35.410 --> 00:36.912
a clue to what happened.

00:37.204 --> 00:38.622
You'd be the first.

00:38.997 --> 00:41.541
I've been fascinated by Terra Nova
since I was a kid, sir.

00:41.791 --> 00:45.420
I always thought lost colonies affected
boomers more than anyone else.

00:45.712 --> 00:48.423
Something about people
who choose to live off-world.

00:50.091 --> 00:51.551
Captain,

00:51.760 --> 00:53.970
do you think anyone's still there?

00:54.846 --> 00:56.306
I'll let you know...

00:56.514 --> 00:58.808
...in about three hours
and 17 minutes.

01:04.397 --> 01:09.736
"It's been a long road
Gettin' from there to here"

01:12.197 --> 01:15.617
"It's been a long time"

01:15.825 --> 01:19.662
"But my time is finally near"

01:19.871 --> 01:24.125
"And I will see my dream
Come alive at last"

01:24.334 --> 01:27.253
"I will touch the sky"

01:27.462 --> 01:31.257
"And they're not gonna
Hold me down no more"

01:31.466 --> 01:34.469
"No, they're not gonna change my mind"

01:34.677 --> 01:39.390
"'Cause I've got faith of the heart"

01:39.599 --> 01:42.518
"I'm going where my heart will take me"

01:42.727 --> 01:47.315
"I've got faith to believe"

01:47.523 --> 01:50.109
"I can do anything"

01:50.318 --> 01:54.822
"I've got strength of the soul"

01:55.031 --> 01:57.909
"And no one's gonna bend or break me"

01:58.117 --> 02:03.456
"I can reach any star"

02:03.831 --> 02:07.585
"I've got faith"

02:07.793 --> 02:11.505
"I've got faith"

02:11.714 --> 02:16.510
"Faith of the heart"

